reviewText: Great video-I even watched the outtakes. What are the chances that you would get to all the churches in the Shenandoah Valley to admire the stained glass windows? here you can see them without leaving the comfort of your home. Accompanied by soothing traditional church music, and explanations from art historians. Fascinating.
Gorgeous! Nicely narrated history of the lovely windows of our Shenandoah Valley plus explanation about stained glass making g along the way!
